<h2>Your Photos</h2>
<p>Many of the problems of the MTA are hidden away out of sight: <a href="http://www.streetsblog.org/2008/07/28/the-biggest-fare-hike-factor-it-could-be-mta-debt/">ballooning debts</a>, <%= link_to 'unnecessary administrators', possibilities_information_path(:anchor => 'bloat') %> and <%= link_to 'missing progress', possibilities_information_path(:anchor => 'coverage') %> can't be captured on camera in the subways.  But sometimes the evidence is in plain sight.  In those cases, it's up to us to collect and share this evidence to further the cause for change.</p>

<p>We appreciate your help in sharing yours, as shining a light on the problems is the first step toward correcting them.  To contribute your photos and videos, upload them to <%= link_to 'Flickr.com', 'http://flickr.com/' %> and tag them with "ourmta-photos".  You can then view them below or <a href="http://www.flickr.com/search/?q=ourmta-photos&amp;m=tags">browse them</a> on Flickr.</p>

